sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant SubscribersUI as Subscribers Dashboard
    participant SubsAPI as /api/subscribers endpoints
    participant DB as PostgreSQL (Prisma)

    Admin->>SubscribersUI: Open /dashboard/subscribers
    SubscribersUI->>SubsAPI: GET /api/subscribers?q=&page=1
    SubsAPI->>DB: Query subscribers with filters
    DB-->>SubsAPI: Paginated subscriber rows
    SubsAPI-->>SubscribersUI: List payload
    SubscribersUI-->>Admin: Render table

    Admin->>SubscribersUI: Delete subscriber row
    SubscribersUI->>SubsAPI: DELETE /api/subscribers/:id
    SubsAPI->>DB: Delete subscriber by id
    DB-->>SubsAPI: Delete result
    SubsAPI-->>SubscribersUI: Success + updated list
